ke":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n欺凌真係死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372da6bda37816cda7ade6aa61de5c8071617b14","tid":2492966,"uid":183844,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"親身體驗<br />\n霸凌真係好撚癲<br />\n手段又可以好撚高<br />\n嗰種狠真係無諗過可以係小朋友做出嚟<br />\n成日話保護小朋友<br />\n有冇諗過呢個社會嘅所謂小朋友心智已經成熟<br />\n嗰種競爭嘅心同仇恨心非常完整<br />\n要保護嘅唔保護<br />\n到出咗事就淨係識話只係一個小朋友"},{"pid":"97442951abfd936b5e7944b877b1d4e2ff1c45b7","tid":2492966,"uid":76563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"母親十分擔心爽彩，所以分別在4-6月找了班主任共4次，但班主任的回應卻是「那些孩子（ABC）是笨蛋而已啦不會做出欺凌的事的」<span class=\"red\">「今天要與男朋友約會，明天再談可以嗎？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天下教蓄一樣黑"},{"pid":"cda49f51feff2892f74e00617cbf71375fb8a135","tid":2492966,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:48:22.000Z","msg":"畜*"},{"pid":"aec3b2da67aa5d2087a281ba56eabe340dc079e5","tid":2492966,"uid":170438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"日本人本身就係咁樣，冰山一角"},{"pid":"876bd77e8dddb58be5b92704cab0acfeec2d80d6","tid":2492966,"uid":198449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"所以少年法都係on9 根本要管 特別係細個個時就要管"},{"pid":"9d0d3e1c57dc66218a74918f333bac958df15afa","tid":2492966,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"可憐乖乖女咁就死咗"},{"pid":"1906ac2c450bffc4a329efa6b3174cf7381c9ac9","tid":2492966,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"876bd77e8dddb58be5b92704cab0acfeec2d80d6","tid":2492966,"uid":198449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"所以少年法都係on9 根本要管 特別係細個個時就要管"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"應該取消少年法，犯法不論年齡一律平等看待"},{"pid":"ed1d3ac98e0dd035afd0d68f64203a89e9f662e6","tid":2492966,"uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"世上冇公義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83da2dfa841f3d97a518a724706f0bf70ea6f30f","tid":2492966,"uid":209198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:53:59.000Z","msg":"真係好撚慘...<br />\n唔好講欺凌<br />\n就算比人講啲閒言碎語已經好難受<br />\n更何況好似呢個妹妹咁俾人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n妹妹妳已經好堅強啦<br />\n辛苦曬你<br />\n安息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3874d0f8df543276782fe1a186b2da21c636b9c0","tid":2492966,"uid":320220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"所以你日本仲係度嘈生育率低<br />\n大佬呀，你下下弱肉強食，有問題又視而不見，我點知生出黎個細路做唔做到勝者?做唔到咪仆街?"}]}